My legs were dead this morning. Don&rsquo;t know if it is the heat or the 40 mile ride Thursday night on the single speed. Hopefully tomorrow&rsquo;s ride will be better. Took some different roads on this Charleston trip. Rode by the airport, Park Circle, and came back home on Dorchester Rd.
